data.chief_complaint: I have been experiencing severe headaches for the past week.
data.history_of_present_illness: The headaches started seven days ago, are mostly localized in the forehead, get worse in bright light and are not relieved by over-the-counter painkillers.
data.family_history: Mother has a history of migraines.
data.social_history: No recent travel and no known exposure to infectious diseases, works from home during the pandemic.
data.review_of_symptoms: Accompanied by nausea, occasional dizziness, but no fever or vision changes.
